{{DISPLAYTITLE:Teleport_ZombieChanger}}
{{Special|39|tid, tag|Teleport|ZombieChanger}}

* ''tid'': Thing ID of the destination spot 
* ''tag'': Tag of destination sector

Teleports the activating thing to a new location, but without fog or a delay. After teleporting, the teleported object switches to its pain state.
If ''tag'' is 0, it will use a random teleport destination out of those with the matching tid. This can be restricted to certain sectors if ''tag''Â non-zero. If ''tid'' is 0 and ''tag'' is non-zero, it will use the first teleport destination found in the first sector with the matching tag.

